---
import SiteLayout from "@/layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="About EveryWordGames - Wordle, Guessing, and Puzzle Games"
  description="Learn about EveryWordGames, a fast local-first platform for Wordle variants, guessing games, word puzzles, stats, and achievements."
  path="/about"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container seo-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">About Us</p>
      <h1>About EveryWordGames.com</h1>
      <p class="lede">Welcome to <strong>everywordgames.com</strong>, the definitive word game website. We are proud to feature all word games available on the market, from classic Wordle variants and multi-board puzzles to hangman, geography guessing, and entertainment clues.</p>
      <p>If you're looking for the ultimate destination to play word games online, you've found it. Our platform is built for speed and replayability. Whether you're hunting for a quick brain teaser or want to spend hours mastering every word game available on the market, <strong>everywordgames.com</strong> is your fast, local-first browser experience.</p>
      <p>Games save stats and achievements locally on your device, allowing you to build streaks across the largest collection of word puzzle games without ever needing an account. Jump in, start guessing, and play every word game out there today.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
